            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's a dance school not good for study. They are playing Bollywood songs with very huge sound daily don't know the purpose. They are mainly focusing on extra curricular activities in school not in study. I really worried how they are playing with student carrier. Even student and their parents know everything but don't know why they are not escalating to school management. Even Admin department\\Security is completely worthless and unprofessional. Daily traffic get choked completely outside gate during school off time. Security are very un professional they don't know how to manage traffic.  They keep stand hand in hand and people staying near school suffer. I am also living near by and lots of people suggested me to get your son admission in this school as it is very near to my residence and transport is not required for this school. But as i saw what is happening daily in this school, I completely denied. I am just suggesting  to other parents.. you are paying money for your child to school with some expectation. So please keep your eyes open, monitor and discuss with your child what is happening. If required highlight your concern to school management it's a matter of your child carrier.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
