            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "If you're doing your ward admission because of less fees, think thrice before taking the decision. In two years, this school destroyed my child self confidence. They just want the students to become book worms, hell lot of school homework, no creativity, no such functions/occasions where parents can do meaningful interaction with teachers or management. Very very outdated conventional teaching approach. Overstressed teachers who are not trained enough to conduct effective PTMs. I discontinued after 2 years and will never ever recommend anyone to get admission here.  Don't compromise with quality as it will cost huge in future.",
